data.description: NET METERING, 22 OWNED SOLAR PANELS, VA ASSUMABLE LOW RATE 2.25%! This spacious 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom house offers the perfect blend of comfort and style. Step inside to discover newly renovated interiors and soaring ceilings that exude modern elegance. The open-concept living area is bathed in natural light, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere.There is a full bedroom and bathroom located on first floor and a separate dining room.The sleek kitchen features stainless steel appliances making it a culinary enthusiast's delight. The spacious primary suite boasts a private renovated en-suite bathroom, providing a tranquil retreat after a long day. With three bathrooms in total, convenience is at your fingertips.  The spacious landscaped backyard has a covered lanai, perfect for outdoor gatherings. The large fenced yard with tropical landscaping is sure to impress! HOA fee includes Cable, Internet and access to fitness center community swimming pool and tennis courts.
